,")",",","-",".","/","0","1","2","2.6","2.6.1","2.6.1.","3","4","404","7",":","<","=",">","@","_","bash","bin","br","built","bzip2","cach","cento","class","code","comment","configur","d","deploy","devel","devop","etc","export","f","figur","found","g","gcc","gdbm","gutter","gz","gzip","h1","headerlink","highlight","hr","href","http","id","instal","ip","keygen","lang","li","libffi","libyaml","line","local","make","ncurs","nginx","ol","openssl","org","p","page","passeng","path","plain","pre","prefix","pro","profil","pub","rail","readlin","rsa","rubi","script","search","sh","shell","span","ssh","step","sudo","t","tabl","tar","td","titl","tr","useradd","usermod","usr","v","variabl","vi","visudo","wget","wheel","wwwget","x","y","yum","z","zlib","zxvf","。","下列","下載","不用","並","位置","使用","使用者","來","修改","做","優先","內容","公私","公鑰","再","到","創建","加入","可","可以","問題","執行","壓縮","夾下","套件","如果","存在","安裝","官網","密碼","尋找","對","就","已","帳號","建立","後","從","所","手動","把","指令","指定","授權","操作","新增","是","時","會安裝","格式","檔","檔並","檔案","權限","沒裝","版本","環境","產生","用","的","相關","確認","簡化","系統","編譯","群組","自動","處理","行為","解壓縮","設定","該","讓","資料","輸入","透過","這個","連線","進入","遠端","部署","鑰","零","需","順利安裝","預設","顯示","｜"],"pipeline":["trimmer","stopWordFilter","stemmer"]},"store":{"/2019/02/15/installing_rails_in_centos_7/":{"url":"/2019/02/15/installing_rails_in_centos_7/","title":"centOS 7 ｜從零部署 Ruby On Rails","tags":["DevOps","Ruby On Rails","Deploy"],"tagArr":[{"name":"DevOps","path":"/tags/DevOps/"},{"name":"Ruby On Rails","path":"/tags/Ruby-On-Rails/"},{"name":"Deploy","path":"/tags/Deploy/"}],"cates":["DevOps"],"cover":"/img/installing_rails_in_centos_7.jpg","desc":"<h1 id=\"Step-0-SSH-遠端連線問題\"><a href=\"#Step-0-SSH-遠端連線問題\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Step.0 SSH 遠端連線問題\"></a>Step.0 SSH 遠端連線問題</h1><ol>\n<li>建立 SSH keygen</li>\n<li>設定公鑰授權<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 產生 SSH 公私鑰</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ ssh-keygen -t rsa</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># ssh 連線指令</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ ssh 帳號@ip位置</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"Step-1-處理使用者權限問題\"><a href=\"#Step-1-處理使用者權限問題\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Step.1 處理使用者權限問題\"></a>Step.1 處理使用者權限問題</h1><ol>\n<li>創建使用者</li>\n<li>把使用者加入群組</li>\n<li>讓該群組使用者不用輸入密碼就可 sudo<br>a. 透過指令 <code>sudo visudo</code> 進入設定檔並加入下列設定<br> <code>%wheel  ALL=(ALL)       ALL</code><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 創建使用者並指定群組 (wheel)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ useradd 使用者 -G wheel</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 修改已存在使用者群組</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ sudo usermod -a -G wheel 使用者</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"Step-2-安裝編譯-Ruby-相關套件\"><a href=\"#Step-2-安裝編譯-Ruby-相關套件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Step.2 安裝編譯 Ruby 相關套件\"></a>Step.2 安裝編譯 Ruby 相關套件</h1><ol>\n<li><p>透過指令安裝編譯所需套件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ sudo yum install -y gcc bzip2 openssl-devel libyaml-devel libffi-devel readline-devel zlib-devel gdbm-devel ncurses-devel</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>到官網下載 Ruby 檔</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 使用 wget (wwwget)指令下載檔案, 如果沒裝 wget 可以用 yum install wget 安裝.</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ wget https://cache.ruby-lang.org/pub/ruby/2.6/ruby-2.6.1.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>解壓縮檔案</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"># tar 是解壓縮指令, -z(使用 Gzip 壓縮格式), -x(解壓縮), -v(顯示檔案內容 ), -f(指定檔案)</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ tar -zxvf ruby-2.6.1.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>編譯 Ruby<br>Ruby 預設會安裝到 <code>/usr/local</code> 的位置, 執行 <code>configure</code> 這個檔案來對 Ruby 編譯時的行為做設定。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ ./configure --prefix=/usr/<span class=\"built_in\">local</span>/ruby-2.6.1pro.d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>進入 Ruby 資料夾下後,使用指令 <code>$ make</code> 編譯 Ruby, 再使用 <code>$ make install</code> 把 Ruby 順利安裝。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>手動執行確認 Ruby 版本</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ /usr/<span class=\"built_in\">local</span>/ruby-2.6.1/bin/ruby -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>透過環境設定簡化操作檔案</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ <span class=\"built_in\">export</span> PATH=/usr/<span class=\"built_in\">local</span>/ruby-2.6.1/bin:<span class=\"variable\">$PATH</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>新增新增 shell script 設定檔讓系統自動優先尋找指定版本 Ruby</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ sudo vi /etc/profile.d/ruby.sh</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 新增下列設定</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">export</span> PATH=/usr/<span class=\"built_in\">local</span>/ruby-2.6.1/bin:<span class=\"variable\">$PATH</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"Step-3-安裝-Passenger-Nginx\"><a href=\"#Step-3-安裝-Passenger-Nginx\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Step.3 安裝 Passenger-Nginx\"></a>Step.3 安裝 Passenger-Nginx</h1>","date":"2019-02-15T10:53:51+08:00","day":"15","month":"二月","authorLink":"github.com/jimmy2822","authorNick":"居米"},"/404.html":{"url":"/404.html","title":"404 Page Not Found","tags":[],"tagArr":[],"cates":[],"cover":"/img/default_cover.jpg","desc":"","date":"2019-02-12T00:00:00+08:00","day":"12","month":"二月","authorLink":"https://github.com/jimmy2822","authorNick":"Jimmy Wu"},"/search/index.html":{"url":"/search/index.html","title":"search","tags":[],"tagArr":[],"cates":[],"cover":"/img/default_cover.jpg","desc":"","date":"2019-02-12T14:35:25+08:00","day":"12","month":"二月","authorLink":"https://github.com/jimmy2822","authorNick":"Jimmy Wu"}}}